      <title>哈佛在警告资金威胁后借了7.5亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/harvard-to-borrow-750-million-after-warning-of-funding-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学计划从华尔街借入7.5亿美元，并在特朗普政府对联邦资金的越来越多的威胁中借入。]]></description>
