    <item>
      <title>美国甚至在特朗普关税之前以34％的职责击中加拿大木材</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/us-hits-canada-lumber-with-34-duties-even-before-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国有望将加拿大软木木材的双重职责降至34.45％，甚至在唐纳德·特朗普总统对该行业签下任何新的关税之前，给美国材料的成本带来了更大的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/us-hits-canada-lumber-with-34-duties-even-before-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 16:07:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的Poilievre说，他将批准Suncor石油项目，地雷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/conservative-leader-poilievre-says-he-would-approve-suncor-oil-project-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党的领导人表示，如果当选，他将加速对10个资源项目的批准，包括延长艾伯塔省的主要Suncor Energy Inc.油砂矿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/conservative-leader-poilievre-says-he-would-approve-suncor-oil-project-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 15:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普指示安全小组审查美国钢铁交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trump-directs-security-panel-to-review-us-steel-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）下令对美国钢铁公司的潜在出售给Nippon Steel Corp.进行另一项审查，开门，修改其前任乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的决定，以阻止141亿美元的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trump-directs-security-panel-to-review-us-steel-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 14:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税时，银行推迟贷款，担心“悬挂”债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/banks-postpone-leveraged-loan-sale-for-hig-s-us-canada-it-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街贷方正在推迟杠杆汇款交易，因为投资者回避风险交易，而全球市场在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的大量关税之后卷入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/banks-postpone-leveraged-loan-sale-for-hig-s-us-canada-it-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:54:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税头条播下混乱的关税头条新闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战争释放的市场混乱持续了第三天，因为股票，债券和商品都疯狂地摇摇欲坠，这既受到经济衰退的担忧和猜测，财务损失都会驱使他改变路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税罗尔市场时，新兴资产暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/emerging-asian-currencies-slip-as-risk-off-extends-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场的股票和货币延长了下降，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易政策的头条新闻使全球市场颠覆了全球市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/emerging-asian-currencies-slip-as-risk-off-extends-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 04:58:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言中国关税加息，欧洲股票低一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-stock-futures-drop-after-worst-week-since-march-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，欧洲股票跌至一年多的最低水平，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对中国和外国领导人发出了新的关税威胁，并在谈判桌上竞争，以说服他降低他的高关税指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-stock-futures-drop-after-worst-week-since-march-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街在关税上被野外挥杆抓住：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波动性的浪潮重新震撼了市场，股票，债券和商品被围绕总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的头条造成混乱而鞭打，这并没有使投资者担心全球经济的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商提高关税头条的第三天掉落，风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/gold-falls-further-at-open-as-traders-assess-tariff-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当贸易商对与唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税政策有关的许多头条新闻反应时，黄金连续第三天倒下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/gold-falls-further-at-open-as-traders-assess-tariff-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
